# Update Profile Detailes Route
POST http://localhost:8080/update_profile_data HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "token":  "52d6fdca4e9f68d4a1bc8e9725aa24a8edcb1ffdb6c156a12aac92b851c116b1",
   "bio": "Hello, I'm User!",
